MODELS
1. Author has_many books
- attributes: name, number of books written

2. Books belong_to author
has_many users through reviews
attributes: author_id, title, rating, number of ratings, pages, genre, year published, date read

-----------------------------
3. User has_many books through reviews
attributes: name, email, pw

4. Reviews
attributes: content, user_id, book_id

PAGES
-list of all books in system... what have others said?
- author - index - authors you have read with books they written plus links
  - show - specific author + books author wrote
  - edit + delete functionality

- books - list of books, read
  - filters on when you read them
